skins.name: Default
skins.secIdle1Text: Last time someone tried to impersonate me, one of my little sisters told them to name EVERY Fletcher-class ship. That's when they gave up the act~
skins.secIdle2Text: When I look at my little sisters, it makes me wonder... Maybe our parents were rabbits?
skins.secIdle3Text: ... Commander? Really... Are you thinking about one of my sisters again?
skins.secTouchText: My little sisters would probably like doing this too. Huh? Your hand would get sore from it?
skins.secSpecialTouchText: C-Commander, please stop! What if my sisters see this...
